:XH3.Display 1 - Work with Questions

:P.
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP STRHQM'.
General Information.
:ELINK.

:P.
The work with questions display enables you to maintain the
questions that where previously created, you are also able to create
a new question by pressing F6=Add.

:P.
Please keep in mind that a question can not be removed if it is
used in a question list and the question was answered during
customer call registration.

:P.
Please read the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP CONQUES OMSCONHD'.
Q&A concepts
:ELINK.
for more information about questions.
