:HELP NAME=OMH00404.General Help For Display 2

:XH3.Display 2 - Maintain Question

:P.
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP STRHQM'.
General Information.
:ELINK.

:P.
The maintain question display enables you to perform actions on
a question. In change mode you are able to change the question. Please
be carefull with this option since a question may be used already.
If you then change the question, it will no longer have meaning
for the Q&A history which is stored with each incident.
:P.
Please read the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP CONQUES OMSCONHD'.
Q&A concepts
:ELINK.
for more information about questions.
:EHELP.

